<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recibo de Nómina - {{employee.name}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #333;
            background: white;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2563eb;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .company-logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            max-height: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .company-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .company-info {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        /* Receipt Info */
        .receipt-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .receipt-number {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }
        
        .receipt-date {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        /* Employee Info */
        .employee-section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .employee-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .employee-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #d1d5db;
        }
        
        .employee-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
        }
        
        .employee-value {
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        /* Period Info */
        .period-section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .period-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        /* Payroll Summary */
        .payroll-summary {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .summary-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .summary-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .summary-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .gross-salary { border-color: #3b82f6; }
        .gross-salary .summary-value { color: #3b82f6; }
        
        .deductions { border-color: #ef4444; }
        .deductions .summary-value { color: #ef4444; }
        
        .net-salary { border-color: #10b981; }
        .net-salary .summary-value { color: #10b981; }
        
        .status { border-color: #f59e0b; }
        .status .summary-value { color: #f59e0b; }
        
        /* Details Tables */
        .details-section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .details-table th {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        }
        
        .details-table td {
            padding: 8px 10px;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .details-table .amount {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .perception-amount {
            color: #10b981;
        }
        
        .deduction-amount {
            color: #ef4444;
        }
        
        /* Totals */
        .totals-section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .totals-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        .totals-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        }
        
        .totals-table .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #f9fafb;
        }
        
        .totals-table .amount {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .final-total {
            background: #1f2937;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        /* Signatures */
        .signatures-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .signatures-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 120px;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #374151;
            margin: 30px 0 10px 0;
            height: 1px;
        }
        
        .signature-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .signature-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
        }
        
        .signature-date {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
        
        /* Print Styles */
        @media print {
            body { font-size: 11px; }
            .container { padding: 15px; }
            .signatures-section { page-break-inside: avoid; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            {{#if company.logo}}
            <img src="{{company.logo}}" alt="Logo" class="company-logo">
            {{/if}}
            <div class="company-name">{{company.name}}</div>
            <div class="company-info">
                {{company.address}}<br>
                Tel: {{company.phone}} | Email: {{company.email}}<br>
                RFC: {{company.rfc}}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Receipt Info -->
        <div class="receipt-info">
            <div>
                <div class="receipt-number">{{receiptNumber}}</div>
                <div class="receipt-date">Recibo de Nómina</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-weight: bold;">Período: {{period.startDate}} - {{period.endDate}}</div>
                <div class="receipt-date">Generado: {{generatedAt}} {{generatedTime}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Employee Information -->
        <div class="employee-section">
            <div class="section-title">Información del Empleado</div>
            <div class="employee-grid">
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Nombre:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.name}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">ID Empleado:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.employeeId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Departamento:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.department}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Puesto:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.position}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">RFC:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.rfc}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">CURP:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.curp}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">IMSS:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.imss}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Cuenta Bancaria:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{employee.bankAccount}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Period Information -->
        <div class="period-section">
            <div class="section-title">Información del Período</div>
            <div class="period-grid">
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Frecuencia:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{period.frequency}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Semana:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{period.weekNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="employee-item">
                    <span class="employee-label">Año:</span>
                    <span class="employee-value">{{period.year}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Payroll Summary -->
        <div class="payroll-summary">
            <div class="section-title">Resumen de Nómina</div>
            <div class="summary-grid">
                <div class="summary-item gross-salary">
                    <div class="summary-label">Salario Bruto</div>
                    <div class="summary-value">${{formatCurrency payroll.grossSalary}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-item deductions">
                    <div class="summary-label">Deducciones</div>
                    <div class="summary-value">${{formatCurrency payroll.totalDeductions}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-item net-salary">
                    <div class="summary-label">Salario Neto</div>
                    <div class="summary-value">${{formatCurrency payroll.netSalary}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-item status">
                    <div class="summary-label">Estado</div>
                    <div class="summary-value">{{payroll.status}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Perceptions Details -->
        {{#if perceptions.length}}
        <div class="details-section">
            <div class="section-title">Percepciones</div>
            <table class="details-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Concepto</th>
                        <th>Descripción</th>
                        <th>Monto</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each perceptions}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{concept}}</td>
                        <td>{{description}}</td>
                        <td class="amount perception-amount">+${{formatCurrency amount}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        <!-- Deductions Details -->
        {{#if deductions.length}}
        <div class="details-section">
            <div class="section-title">Deducciones</div>
            <table class="details-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Concepto</th>
                        <th>Descripción</th>
                        <th>Monto</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each deductions}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{concept}}</td>
                        <td>{{description}}</td>
                        <td class="amount deduction-amount">-${{formatCurrency amount}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        <!-- Totals -->
        <div class="totals-section">
            <table class="totals-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Salario Base:</td>
                    <td class="amount">${{formatCurrency payroll.calculatedSalary}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Total Percepciones:</td>
                    <td class="amount">${{formatCurrency payroll.totalPerceptions}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Total Deducciones:</td>
                    <td class="amount">${{formatCurrency payroll.totalDeductions}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="final-total">
                    <td class="label">TOTAL A PAGAR:</td>
                    <td class="amount">${{formatCurrency payroll.netSalary}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Signatures -->
        <div class="signatures-section">
            <div class="section-title">Firmas de Conformidad</div>
            <div class="signatures-grid">
                <div class="signature-box">
                    <div class="signature-label">Firma del Empleado</div>
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-name">{{signatures.employeeName}}</div>
                    <div class="signature-date">{{signatures.employeeDate}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="signature-box">
                    <div class="signature-label">Firma de Recursos Humanos</div>
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-name">{{signatures.hrName}}</div>
                    <div class="signature-date">{{signatures.hrDate}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Este recibo de nómina ha sido generado electrónicamente y es válido sin firma autógrafa.</p>
            <p>Para consultas o aclaraciones, contacte al departamento de Recursos Humanos.</p>
            <p>Documento generado el {{generatedAt}} a las {{generatedTime}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
